Subject: [PATCH] coretext: replace MSZ glyphs with halfwidth variants

---
 include/aribcaption/renderer.h          |   4 +-
 src/renderer/text_renderer_coretext.cpp | 151 +++++++++++++++++++++++-
 src/renderer/text_renderer_coretext.hpp |   4 +
 3 files changed, 154 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)

diff --git a/include/aribcaption/renderer.h b/include/aribcaption/renderer.h
